General.Name: Attendo International publ AB
General.Description: Attendo AB (publ) provides care in Sweden, Finland, Norway, and Denmark. The company offers nursing homes and home care services for older people; and disability care services, which includes group homes and supportive housing, and daily activities including respite care and short-term accommodation. It also provides social psychiatry service; and individual and family care including social-worker supported foster care, crisis and emergency accommodation, HVB-homes, addiction care, and other supportive housing services. The company was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Danderyd, Sweden.
